channel.title: What would be a good 614+ base?
channel.description:
i was using rscalifornia 711 when it got released and fixed the anti-leech but after readding barrows and half assing soulwars i noticed how its handling all these processes in a different way it seems like this will cause terrible lagg and alot of cpu will be used when 60+ players will be using this
well im fairly new to 602+ bases i just got into this since i moved on from project insanity 317 loading 614 :\ so will anyone suggest me a stable source loading 614+? like i said im new to this
now if we talk about 317's i know id be suggested hyperion & apollo so yeah :)
